data %<>% mutate(date = dmy(date))

data %<>% rename(evn_infl = evn_inflmood)
moodnames <- select(data, contains("mood")) %>% names

moodgroups = list(g1 = moodnames[1:4],
              g2 = moodnames[5:8],
              g3 = moodnames[9:13])

get_mood_group <- function(char){
  for(i in 1:3){
    if(char %in% moodgroups[[i]]){return(i)}
  }
  return(NA)
}

map(moodnames, 
    ~data %>%
  ggplot() + 
    geom_point(
      aes_string(x = "date", 
                 y = .x), 
      position = "jitter"
      )
  )
